    <item>
      <title>阿根廷寻求200亿美元IMF交易的大部分</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/argentina-seeks-large-portion-of-20-billion-imf-deal-up-front</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉此事的人们说，阿根廷正在寻求前期付款，该付款代表其未来200亿美元计划的大部分计划与国际货币基金组织有关，因为谈判现在集中于支付的规模和时间安排。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/argentina-seeks-large-portion-of-20-billion-imf-deal-up-front</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 18:22:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Memecoins，Stablecoins，24/7银行，SEC主席的Robinhood CEO</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-27/robinhood-ceo-on-stablecoins-24-7-banking-sec-chair-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Robinhood CEO Vlad Tenev讨论了Memecoins，Stablecoins，24/7交易以及公司新银行章节，包括支票和储蓄帐户。弗拉德在接受Scarlet Fu和Sonali Basak采访时说，如果要确认为SEC主席，他对Paul Atkins非常乐观。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-27/robinhood-ceo-on-stablecoins-24-7-banking-sec-chair-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 18:15:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国摇摇欲坠的恢复被认为有自动关税的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/germany-s-shaky-recovery-at-risk-from-auto-tariffs-be-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据彭博经济学的说法，唐纳德·特朗普总统决定对所有自动进口征收25％的关税，这危害德国从停滞期间的恢复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/germany-s-shaky-recovery-at-risk-from-auto-tariffs-be-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 18:01:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前商业秒。罗斯在关税，马诺，欧洲的增值税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-27/former-commerce-sec-ross-on-tariffs-doge-europe-s-vat-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[威尔伯·罗斯（Wilbur Ross）曾在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的第一家内阁中担任商务部长，他讨论了美国公司吸收关税，欧洲法规和增值税的能力，以及与彭博社的Kriti Gupta有关的政府效率。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-27/former-commerce-sec-ross-on-tariffs-doge-europe-s-vat-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 18:00:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场在信用中具有弹性：poli</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-27/markets-are-resilient-in-credit-poli-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Oaktree Capital Management的共同竞争经理Danielle Poli说，市场具有信贷弹性，并将防御部门（例如食品和饮料）视为高收益信贷的避风港。她在彭博社上与彭博社上的猩红色Fu进行了交谈。

 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-27/markets-are-resilient-in-credit-poli-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 17:57:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比奥警告委内瑞拉不要进攻圭亚那，埃克森</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/rubio-warns-venezuala-against-attacking-guyana-exxon-projects</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿马可·卢比奥（Marco Rubio）警告委内瑞拉，任何企图入侵圭亚那或威胁埃克森美孚公司在该国的行动的尝试都是“非常糟糕的举动”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/rubio-warns-venezuala-against-attacking-guyana-exxon-projects</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 17:49:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汽车制造商在美国高级市场上迈出了税款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/car-makers-trail-us-high-grade-market-with-tariffs-set-to-hit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统对汽车进口的25％关税并警告未来一场更广泛的贸易战后，汽车制造商的债券在美国债务市场中削弱了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/car-makers-trail-us-high-grade-market-with-tariffs-set-to-hit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 16:28:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>下注美国弱点正在推动新兴市场的集会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/bets-on-us-weakness-are-fueling-a-rally-across-emerging-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些投资者押注美好时光只是为了开始新兴市场，因为对美国经济的担忧增强了长期遭受苦难的资产类别的魅力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/bets-on-us-weakness-are-fueling-a-rally-across-emerging-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 00:42:51 GMT</pubDate>
